        "content": "KEYBOARD MACROS"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Keyboard macros are recording of keyboard events (ie: data keys,"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "terminal functions, and primary commands) sequentially ordered"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "for later playback to repetatively perform a specific action."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Key macros are typically assigned to specific keys, and are"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "invoked whenever the key is pressed."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "For details, select from the following by number:"
